        "subject": "LU-3274 osc: allow to call brw_commit() multiple times",
        "message": "LU-3274 osc: allow to call brw_commit() multiple times\n\nSometimes the rq_commit_cb of BRW RPC can be called twice if that RPC\nhas already committed at reply time. This will cause inaccuracy of\nunstable pages accounting and then assertion.\n\nThis patch is back-ported from the following one:\nLustre-commit: ab391baa6c9f005b84454e1398ea1b8f77095615\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/8215\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie9a173a9c9ee78126759f424dc2c77462f1ca667\n"
